I have thought about it alot since they started this class balance stuff. I belive when VI started this newest round of class balance for all classes they had the best intentions, but when they looked at wizards  closely ie effectivness in Velious,  and resist rates.  Then they looked at overall Damage and then they compared it to other classes and at some point they realized we were right and then proceeded to try to think of a fix but in my opinion they cannot think of a fix that wont piss off other classes and get them saying some of the things we are saying now.  I  sincerly feel that they would rather ignore us lose some of us then to upset other classes who are relatively happy.<br>
<br>
So to me in conclusion they lose the least amount of money ignoreing us and keeping the other classes feeling balanced. <br>
<br>
